Protecting shared actor arrays from concurrent writing crashes:

```cpp
#include <thread>
#include <mutex>
#include <vector>

std::vector<int> SharedActiveActorIDs;
std::mutex ActorIDsMutex;

void AddActorID_ThreadSafe(int NewID) {
    // lock_guard locks mutex on creation and unlocks it automatically when exiting scope
    std::lock_guard<std::mutex> Lock(ActorIDsMutex);
    SharedActiveActorIDs.push_back(NewID); 
}
```
